{
  "id": "adv_card_ski_03_01",
  "title": "白石沙季 1話 自分をさらけ出す",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（今は、月ストのレッスン中だったな）\n（みんな元気に練習してるだろうか）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Right now‚ it's the middle of Moon Tempest's lesson)\n(I wonder if everyone is practicing energetically)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 8.5473241806
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "……あっ！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ah!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.5973241806,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんなさい、今のところ\nもう一回お願いします！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry‚ this part‚\ncan we do it again?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.9306575139,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "こ、今度はどうでしょうか\nステップにミスはなかったと……思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "H-How about this time?\nI don't think there were any mistakes in the steps…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "……そうですか……はい\nもう一度、お願いします！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I see… Okay.\nPlease let me do it again!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "……ミスがないだけではダメ\nお客さんに情熱が伝わらないと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…It's not enough to just avoid mistakes.\nIf the audience can't feel my passion…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（東京に来てから沙季のパフォーマンスは良くなってる）\n（ここで、もうひと皮むけることが出来れば……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Saki's performance has improved since coming to Tokyo)\n(If she can have another breakthrough here…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.4333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8166.666666700003,
          "startTime": 43.5
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん！\nお疲れ様です、レッスン見に来て下さったんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san!\nThank you for coming to watch the lesson.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、沙季もお疲れ様\n月ストの他のみんなは？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ Saki‚ good job.\nWhat about the other members of Moon Tempest?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "今日のグループレッスンは終わりました\n私は……その、もう少し練習をしたくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today's group lesson is over.\nI… um‚ wanted to practice a little more‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "先生に付き合っていただいて\n個人レッスンを受けていたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "so I stayed with the teacher\nand had a private lesson.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そうなのか……\n大分ハードな練習みたいだけど、大丈夫か？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see…\nIt seems like a pretty tough practice‚ but are you okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、このくらい平気です\n練習して、上達していくのは楽しいですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I'm fine with this level of practice.\nPracticing and improving is enjoyable for me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "でも私、まだまだで……\nさっきも先生に何度も注意を受けてしまって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I still have a long way to go…\nI've been scolded by the teacher multiple times earlier too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "注意するところが多いというのは\nそれだけ成長の余地が沢山ある、ということだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Having many areas to be scolded in\nmeans there's a lot of room for growth.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01-ski011.m4a",
      "text": "……ありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Thank you very much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01-ski012.m4a",
      "text": "ただ……もちろん、頑張ってはいるんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "However… of course‚ I am doing my best…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01-ski013.m4a",
      "text": "先生からは、振り付けをなぞっているだけで\n情熱が感じられないと言われてしまって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But the teacher says I'm just mimicking the choreography\nand they can't feel my passion.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01-ski014.m4a",
      "text": "真面目なだけじゃダメ、もっと弾けなさい、とか\n自分をさらけ出しなさいとか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They say being serious is not enough‚ I should be more vibrant‚ or\nI should expose myself more.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "自分をさらけ出す、か……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Expose yourself‚ huh…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01-ski015.m4a",
      "text": "はい。でも、月のテンペストの一員である以上\nステージ上で私が好き勝手する訳にはいきませんし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. But as a member of Moon Tempest‚\nI can't do whatever I want on stage.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01-ski016.m4a",
      "text": "私は、どんな風に頑張ればいいんでしょう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How should I strive to be better?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（自分をさらけ出す、か。言葉にするのは簡単だけど）\n（沙季のような真面目な子には、難しいかもな……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Expose yourself‚ huh? It's easy to say‚ but…)\n(For someone as serious as Saki‚ it might be difficult…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01-ski017.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、ごめん、考えごとをしていて\nそうだな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ sorry‚ I was lost in thought.\nWell…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "本当にただの思いつきなんだけど\n例えば、ロックなんかを参考にしてみるのはどうだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's really just a random idea‚\nbut what if you try taking inspiration from rock?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01-ski018.m4a",
      "text": "ロック、ですか\n……私、あまり聴いたことがありません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rock‚ you say?\n…I haven't really listened to it much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "『ロックだ』なんて言い方もするし\nほら、反抗的だったり、我が道を行く生き方を",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They say things like \"rock spirit\"\nIt means being rebellious‚ going your own way",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "ステージで弾けるって意味なら、参考になるかも\n……って、沙季、聞いてるか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If it means being able to express yourself on stage‚ it might be helpful.\n…Hey‚ Saki‚ are you listening?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01-ski019.m4a",
      "text": "我が道を行く……弾ける……反抗的……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Going my own way… expressing myself… rebellious…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 183.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_01-ski020.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど……",
      "translations": {
