      "text": "ふふふふっ深夜にアイスを食べるだなんて……\n私、なんていけないことをしてるのかしら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehehe… Eating ice cream late at night…\nWhat a bad thing am I doing…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 223.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
