      "text": "今日は、みんなが脱ぎっぱなしにしていた靴も\n片付けてあげないで、放っておいちゃったし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today‚ everyone left their shoes lying around\nand I didn't bother to clean them up…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 236.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
